## Backgrounds & Overlays

### Background page (landing)
```tsx
<div className="relative min-h-screen bg-[#060608] overflow-x-clip">
  {/* Radial gradient chaud */}
  <div className="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style={{ background: "radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(255,171,0,0.06) 0%, rgba(204,136,0,0.02) 40%, transparent 70%)" }} />
  {/* Gold bloom central */}
  <div className="fixed top-[-200px] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1200px] h-[800px] pointer-events-none opacity-[0.045]"
    style={{ background: "radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #FFAB00 0%, transparent 65%)", filter: "blur(80px)" }} />
  {/* Blobs animés */}
  <div className="fixed ... pointer-events-none opacity-[0.03] animate-aurora-1" />
  <div className="fixed ... pointer-events-none opacity-[0.025] animate-aurora-2" />
  {/* Vignette */}
  <div className="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style={{ background: "radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 70% at 50% 50%, transparent 0%, #060608 100%)" }} />
  {/* Overlays texture */}
  <div className="noise-overlay" />
  <div className="grid-overlay" />
</div>
```
- **IMPORTANT** : Utiliser `overflow-x-clip` (PAS `overflow-hidden`) pour ne pas casser `position: sticky`
- Les blobs gold sont animés avec `animate-aurora-1`, `animate-aurora-2`

### Glow section (ambiance gold locale)
```tsx
<div className="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]"
  style={{ background: "radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #FFAB00 0%, transparent 60%)" }} />
```

