## Animations — Framer Motion

### Pattern d'entrée au scroll (section)
```tsx
const ref = useRef(null);
const inView = useInView(ref, { once: true, margin: "-80px" });

<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 30 }}
  animate={inView ? { opacity: 1, y: 0 } : {}}
  transition={{ duration: 0.7, ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }}
>
```

### Easing standard
- **Expo ease-out** : `[0.16, 1, 0.3, 1]` — pour toutes les animations d'apparition
- **Simple** : `"easeOut"` — pour les hovers et micro-interactions

### Stagger pattern (éléments en cascade)
```tsx
{items.map((item, i) => (
  <motion.div
    initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
    animate={inView ? { opacity: 1, y: 0 } : {}}
    transition={{ delay: 0.2 + i * 0.1, duration: 0.6, ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }}
  />
))}
```
- Delay initial : `0.1` à `0.3`
- Incrément par item : `0.08` à `0.15`

### Entrée depuis les côtés
- Gauche : `initial={{ opacity: 0, x: -30 }}` → `animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }}`
- Droite : `initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 30 }}`
- Marquee rows : `x: ±80`

### Scale entrance (cards pricing, floating cards)
```tsx
initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 50, scale: 0.92 }}
animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0, scale: 1 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.8, ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }}
```

### Hover card
```tsx
whileHover={{ y: -6, transition: { duration: 0.25 } }}
```

### AnimatePresence (tabs, accordion, changement de contenu)
```tsx
<AnimatePresence mode="wait">
  <motion.div
    key={activeKey}
    initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12 }}
    animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
    exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -8 }}
    transition={{ duration: 0.25, ease: "easeOut" }}
  />
</AnimatePresence>
```

### Accordion open/close
```tsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}
  animate={{ height: "auto", opacity: 1 }}
  exit={{ height: 0, opacity: 0 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }}
  className="overflow-hidden"
/>
```

### Scroll-jacking (sticky + useScroll)
```tsx
const { scrollYProgress } = useScroll({ target: containerRef, offset: ["start start", "end end"] });
// Container: height = steps * 50vh
// Content: position sticky, top 0, h-screen
// Map scrollYProgress → activeStep
```

### Logo animation (stagger lettres)
- Chaque lettre : `delay: i * 0.05, duration: 0.35, ease: "easeOut"`
- Mouvement : `y: 6 → 0`, `opacity: 0 → 1`

